twelve parsecsNew Achievement: piracy is not the problem	New Achievement: you don’t have to be pretty to kick assLots of changes and fixes!Be sure to check out our official community group and forum for more details.Thanks for the support!																						关于这款游戏							Killing zombies never gets old, but sometimes you just need a break.   Get back to some serious old-school gaming with Syder Arcade!  Syder Arcade is a love letter to Amiga games of the ‘90s, no coins, no upgrade grinding, just your tenacity and a motherload of alien invaders.   Syder Arcade is a free scrolling, multi directional shoot 'em up, an uncompromised old-school experience, furious, challenging, and straightforward. This game will bring you back in time, when bulky starships were cool and games were about player skill and swearing madly at your computer.						
